Package: statsdata
Title: Datasets for Teaching Statistics
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Emily", "Somerset", email = "emily.somerset@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A curated, searchable collection of datasets designed
    specifically for teaching statistics, with metadata describing
    relevant statistical methods, teaching concepts, variable types,
    and course level. Companion to the statsdata-hub website.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
